{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1780129650429,"sessionID":"ses_18801b231ffe1T23Rry15kpUZw","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_01_OswH7PaL4RQFapwEbvs35993","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/plan.md"},"output":"<path>/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/plan.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: <!-- SPECKIT_TEMPLATE_SOURCE: spec-core | v2.2 -->\n2: <!-- SPECKIT_LEVEL: 1 -->\n3: \n4: # Plan — Phase 001: Skill-benchmark deep research\n5: \n6: ## Approach\n7: Run a 20-iteration multi-model deep-research sweep (5 each: MiniMax-2.7, DeepSeek-v4-pro, GPT-5.5-xhigh-fast, Opus-4.8-native), 2 executors in parallel, each iteration a LEAF @deep-research pass writing its own packet; then synthesize a cross-model `research/research.md`.\n8: \n9: ## Steps\n10: 1. Initialize packet-local research state (config, strategy charter with RQ1–RQ7, JSONL).\n11: 2. Dispatch 20 iterations via a background `xargs -P 2` worker pool (one executor per iteration sandbox); salvage replies into iteration `.md` when in-repo writes are blocked.\n12: 3. Stitch per-model `state-parts/*` into `deep-research-state.jsonl`.\n13: 4. Synthesize all 20 iterations into `research/research.md` (per-RQ, cross-model, recommended design + rename map + next steps).\n14: \n15: ## Verification\n16: All 4 models reach 5/5 iteration `.md` files; `research/research.md` present with the required sections; `orchestration-status.log` shows every iteration `exit=0`.\n\n(End of file - total 16 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"<!-- SPECKIT_TEMPLATE_SOURCE: spec-core | v2.2 -->\n<!-- SPECKIT_LEVEL: 1 -->\n\n# Plan — Phase 001: Skill-benchmark deep research\n\n## Approach\nRun a 20-iteration multi-model deep-research sweep (5 each: MiniMax-2.7, DeepSeek-v4-pro, GPT-5.5-xhigh-fast, Opus-4.8-native), 2 executors in parallel, each iteration a LEAF @deep-research pass writing its own packet; then synthesize a cross-model `research/research.md`.\n\n## Steps\n1. Initialize packet-local research state (config, strategy charter with RQ1–RQ7, JSONL).\n2. Dispatch 20 iterations via a background `xargs -P 2` worker pool (one executor per iteration sandbox); salvage replies into iteration `.md` when in-repo writes are blocked.\n3. Stitch per-model `state-parts/*` into `deep-research-state.jsonl`.\n4. Synthesize all 20 iterations into `research/research.md` (per-RQ, cross-model, recommended design + rename map + next steps).\n\n## Verification\nAll 4 models reach 5/5 iteration `.md` files; `research/research.md` present with the required sections; `orchestration-status.log` shows every iteration `exit=0`.","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/plan.md","time":{"start":1780129650416,"end":1780129650428}},"id":"prt_e77fed431001RyA4j32T80PQpv","sessionID":"ses_18801b231ffe1T23Rry15kpUZw","messageID":"msg_e77fec2bc001BtErD4eFxkDlNS"}}
